description:
A girl from Domremy Village on West Star. She`s awakened to her power, "Revelations", the ability to see mysterious visions. People have misunderstood her power as something that bring misfortune, but she gains foresight of a "Savior" who will appear to save their world. In order to carve her own destiny, she pays a visit to East Star.
Source: ANN
name: Jeanne Kaguya d`Arc
